videoDetails.Title: Mother Cat Drinks Lots of Coffee to Get By #funny #catlover #cuteanimals #cartoon
videoDetails.Description:
A hilarious short cartoon about a mother cat that drinks lots of coffee to be able to perform enormous amount of chores and tasks. Coffee makes her perform with super human speed and intensity: she vacuums, feeds the baby, drives to work, writes documents, makes copies, cooks dinner, soothes the baby to sleep and wipes the floor - she sure is one busy mother.
